{"content": "I need to multiply 463 \u00d7 686 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 463\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 324 + 54 + 3 = 381\u2081\u2080\n- 686\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 6\u00d71 = 486 + 72 + 6 = 564\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 381 \u00d7 564 = 214,884\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 214884 \u00f7 9 = 23876 r 0\n- 23876 \u00f7 9 = 2652 r 4\n- 2652 \u00f7 9 = 294 r 6\n- 294 \u00f7 9 = 32 r 6\n- 32 \u00f7 9 = 3 r 5\n- 3 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 3\n\nReading from bottom to top: **356640\u2089**\n\n356640", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 344}